<chapter id=Tasks>Audio Tasks
	<idx>mouse, using a<\idx>
	<idx>keyboard, using a<\idx>

These instructions assume that you are using a mouse.  Most tasks can
also be done without a mouse.  See <link
hyperlink="IntromgrDesktopKeyboardNav" Jump>Keyboard Shortcuts for the
Desktop<\link> for more information.

